de.oaam.model.oaam.library

Interface FunctionInputState

  • All Superinterfaces:
    BoolA, org.eclipse.emf.ecore.EObject, org.eclipse.emf.common.notify.Notifier, OaamBaseElementA

    public interface FunctionInputState
extends BoolA, OaamBaseElementA
    A representation of the model object 'Function Input State'. A link between a Boolean expression and the state of the input. This Boolean is considered to be true if the input has the state defined within.

    The following features are supported:

    • State
    • Input
    See Also:
    de.oaam.model.oaam.library.LibraryPackage#getFunctionInputState()
